OL,3,CUS hospital pauses IVF treatment after
OL,4,Cruling claims frozen embryos are
OL,5,Cchildren
OL,7,FAlabama's largest hospital has paused
OL,8,Fin vitro fertilisation (IVF)
OL,9,Ftreatments in the wake of a court
OL,10,Fruling that claimed frozen embryos are
OL,11,Flegally children.
OL,13,FThe University of Alabama at
OL,14,FBirmingham health system said in a
OL,15,Fstatement it must now evaluate whether
OL,16,Fits patients or doctors could face
OL,17,Fcriminal charges or punitive damages
OL,18,Ffor undergoing treatments.
