OL,7,F"We are saddened that this will impact
OL,8,Four patients' attempt to have a baby
OL,9,Fthrough IVF," the statement read.
OL,11,FDoctors and patients have been
OL,12,Fgrappling with a ruling by the all-
OL,13,FRepublican Alabama Supreme Court that
OL,14,Fquestioned the rights of an embryo.
OL,16,FHave you heard our new podcast Talking
