OL,4,Cruling claims frozen embryos are
OL,5,Cchildren
OL,7,FOn Friday, it ruled the state
OL,8,Frecognises the "rights of the unborn
OL,9,Fchild" and said three couples could
OL,10,Fsue for wrongful death when their
OL,11,Ffrozen embryos were destroyed in a
OL,12,Faccident at a storage facility.
OL,14,FWhile the court case centred on
OL,15,Fwhether embryos were covered under the
OL,16,Fwrongful death of a minor statute,
OL,17,Fsome said treating the embryo as a
OL,18,Fchild, rather than property, could
OL,19,Fhave broader implications and call
OL,20,Finto question many of the practices of
OL,21,FIVF.
