OL,5,Cchildren
OL,7,F"Unborn children are 'children' ...
OL,8,Fwithout exception based on
OL,9,Fdevelopmental stage, physical
OL,10,Flocation, or any other ancillary
OL,11,Fcharacteristics," Justice Jay Mitchell
OL,12,Fwrote of the case.
OL,14,F"Disbelief, denial, all the stages of
OL,15,Fgrief. ... I was stunned," said Dr
OL,16,FMichael Allemand, a reproductive
OL,17,Fendocrinologist at Alabama Fertility,
OL,18,Fwhich provides IVF services.
OL,20,FAllemand said they are having daily
OL,21,Fdiscussions about how to proceed.
