OL,7,FHe said IVF is often the best
OL,8,Ftreatment for patients who desperately
OL,9,Fwant a child, and the ruling threatens
OL,10,Fdoctors' ability to provide that care.
OL,12,F"The moments that our patients are
OL,13,Fwanting to have by growing their
OL,14,Ffamilies - Christmas mornings with
OL,15,Fgrandparents, kindergarten, going in
OL,16,Fthe first day of school, with little
OL,17,Fback-backs - all that stuff is what
OL,18,Fthis is about. Those are the real
OL,19,Fmoments that this ruling could deprive
OL,20,Fpatients of," he said.
